title: LIVE 140 - Beethoven - پلی لیست لایو
description:
" لودویگ فان بتهوون "

سلام من مختار رزمجو هستم

 Playlist | اینجا پادکست پلی لیست

 عنوان : لودویگ فان بتهوون 

 مود : آرامش بخش / بیکلام / کلاسیک

 ژانر: کلاسیک / بیکلام

 تو این اپیزود برترین آثار لودویگ فان بتهوون رو میشنوید

http://hamibash.com/playlistpodcast

https://t.me/playlistpodcas

01-Piano Sonata No. 14 in C-Sharp Minor, Op. 27_2 _Moonlight__ I. Adagio Sostenuto

02-Bagatelle in A Minor, WoO 59, _Für Elise_

03-Beethoven - Emil Gilels - Piano Sonata №8 Pathetic - Rondo

04-Piano Sonata No. 14 in C-Sharp Minor, Op. 27_2 (Moonlight)_ III. Presto

05-Sonata No. 17 in D Minor for Piano, Op. 31_2 (The Tempest)_ III. Allegretto

06-Sonata No. 20 in G Major for Piano, Op. 49_2_ I. Allegro ma non troppo

07-Variations on _Rule Britannia_ in D Major for Piano, WoO 79

08-Valentina Lisitsa - Beethoven- Turkish March, Op. 113 No. 4

09-Zvjezdana Bašić - Ludwig Van Beethoven- Sonata Op. 53 U C-Duru 'Waldstein'- Introduzione

10-Henryk Szeryng, Bernard Haitink, Royal Concertgebouw Orchestra [Orchestra] - 3. Rondo (Allegro)

11-Twelve Contredanses for Orchestra, WoO 14_ Dance No. 12

12-String Quartet No. 8 in E Minor, Op. 59_2, _Razumovsky Quartet No. 2__ III. Allegretto

13-Symphony No. 5 in C Minor, Op. 67, _Fate__ I. Allegro con brio

14-Symphony No. 9 in D Minor, Op. 125 _Choral__ II. Molto vivace

15-Charles T. Cozens - Symphony No. 9 in D Minor, Ode to Joy

16-Sigala, RITA ORA - You for Me
